Module fi.tuni.monitor
Package fi.tuni.monitor.models

Class CoordinateSelectionModel

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.monitor.models.CoordinateSelectionModel
public class CoordinateSelectionModel extends Object
Model for handling coordinate selection related data and operations
Is a part of the MVC pattern, implemented as a singleton to provide convenient access to the data from anywhere
